fu.util

Class ByteRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • fu.util.ByteRecord

  • public class ByteRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    ByteRecords are very memory efficient containers for field-oriented data. This class allows to read such a structure from a byte[].
